{"title":"OBS下载及使用","uid":"dac023327b3074169eff25e09c8e12e1","slug":"OBS下载及使用","date":"2020-08-22T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2021-04-30T13:13:48.392Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/OBS下载及使用.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h1><blockquote>\n<p>OBS作为一个nb，免费，开源，全能的软件，强烈建议使用!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"install-for-windows\"><a href=\"#install-for-windows\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"install for windows\"></a>install for windows</h3><p><a href=\"https://cdn-fastly.obsproject.com/downloads/OBS-Studio-25.0.8-Full-Installer-x64.exe\">点击下载</a></p>\n<p>可能有点慢，强烈建议使用<code>迅雷下载</code></p>\n<p>点击安装包</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gi13jgqeq4j303s07it8w.jpg\"></p>\n<p>然后一直按回车就可以了</p>\n<h3 id=\"install-for-mac\"><a href=\"#install-for-mac\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"install for mac\"></a>install for mac</h3><p><a href=\"https://cdn-fastly.obsproject.com/downloads/obs-mac-25.0.8.dmg\">点击下载</a></p>\n<p>打开后看到</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gi13ya78egj31080rcn7f.jpg\"></p>\n<p>将</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gi13zwk223j308a088gmj.jpg\"></p>\n<p>拖到</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gi13zdefmoj308008aq3v.jpg\"></p>\n<p>就装完了</p>\n<h3 id=\"install-for-ubuntu\"><a href=\"#install-for-ubuntu\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"install for ubuntu\"></a>install for ubuntu</h3><p>终端输入</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> add-apt-repository ppa:obsproject/obs-studio\n$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> update\n$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> upgrade\n$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> obs-studio<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>对于<code>kali linux</code>忽略第一行加仓库的命令。</p>\n<h3 id=\"How-to-use-OBS\"><a href=\"#How-to-use-OBS\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"How to use OBS\"></a>How to use OBS</h3><p>无论使用什么方式打开<code>OBS</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gi1441dmy3j31c00u0wos.jpg\"></p>\n<p>找到最下面的来源</p>\n<p>点击下方<code>+</code>号</p>\n<p>点击</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gi146q0xa6j307a0103yf.jpg\"></p>\n<p>再次点击<code>+</code>号</p>\n<p>依次添加</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gi14860ah2j307q03egls.jpg\"></p>\n<p>这样就可以见到无限递归了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gi14d1dr2hj319m0u0qb0.jpg\"></p>\n<p>点击最右边的<code>设置</code></p>\n<p>找到输出，将<code>录制格式</code>改为<code>mp4</code></p>\n<p>找到热键，添加开始录制和结束录制的快捷键</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gi14k2ruw8j30rg0m2goo.jpg\"></p>\n<p>调整一波图像</p>\n<p>按下<code>ctrl + shift + B</code></p>\n<p>播放你的<code>ppt</code>,介绍你的新闻</p>\n<p>按下<code>ctrl + shift + E</code></p>\n<p>结束录制</p>\n<h3 id=\"Where-is-the-file\"><a href=\"#Where-is-the-file\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Where is the file\"></a>Where is the file</h3><h6 id=\"windows\"><a href=\"#windows\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"windows\"></a>windows</h6><p>打开目录<code>C:\\Users\\你的用户\\Videos</code></p>\n<h5 id=\"mac\"><a href=\"#mac\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"mac\"></a>mac</h5><p>终端输入</p>\n<p><code>open ~/Movies/</code></p>\n<p>就可以看到文件了</p>\n<p>展示一下<a href=\"https://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNDgxMjcwNzg4NA==.html\">我的</a></p>\n","feature":null,"text":"前言 OBS作为一个nb，免费，开源，全能的软件，强烈建议使用! install for windows点击下载 可能有点慢，强烈建议使用迅雷下载 点击安装包 然后一直按回车就可以了 install for mac点击下载 打开后看到 将 拖到 就装完了 install for ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":581,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"OBS","slug":"OBS","count":1,"path":"api/tags/OBS